/**
 * lib/seedDemo.ts — DEMO DATA ONLY.
 *
 * ⚠️  None of the data produced by this module represents real
 * financial records. Every number is generated by a deterministic
 * seeded random walk + a few hand-tuned spikes. This module is the
 * single source of demo data for the WalletSync frontend; running it
 * never touches a real wallet, a real account, or a real customer.
 *
 * Used by:
 *   - scripts/seed-demo-data.mjs (CLI)
 *   - POST /api/persona/switch (in-app dropdown)
 *
 * Both call into the same `seedDemo(persona, days)` so the shape and
 * values are identical regardless of which path produced the data.
 *
 * Personas: freelancer | small_business | student
 *   See PERSONAS below for the per-persona baseline, volatility,
 *   drift, and spike cadence.
 */

